object.descriptionOfTeam:
Welcome to Group Therapy! Please grab a coffee and state your name. We are ultimately a casual hots bunch, but are getting competitive for NGS! We are always looking for a solid tank player to round out our roster, but are open to all roles. We like to experiment in terms of comp, so feel free to bring the weirder heroes. We value having a good time, but when it comes to practice and competition we are looking for respectful individuals that can bring good communication and punctuality to the table. We understand that life happens and scheduling conflicts arise, but being on time (and sober) for practices/games is valued highly. 

The average rank of our squad is about mid to high silver. If you are looking for a group that will support you and help you learn new roles, heroes and playstyles, we are the group for you!

questionnaire.divisionPlacement: I believe we should drop down to Div B. We are losing our main DPS carry and trying a new Tank player (Peas) who has Ping. In Nexo we were playing in Group 2 and games have been competitive but very difficult.
questionnaire.priorPlacement: Last season I think we were in the right division, it was very competitive and although we lost first round playoffs, it seemed very possible.
questionnaire.otherLeagues: Nexomania Group 2 (second from highest). We won 1 game and the others were pretty 1 sided wins by the other team.
questionnaire.otherInfo: Back when Pepegas on Ice won Div B, we were playing 3 times a week and we had BishopMist and Jakeyaz who were both strong players. Now we play closer to 1.5 times a week and are trying out new roles.

object.descriptionOfTeam: we have particpated in rcc tourneys and partook in ngs season 14 and got to finals for div e east.

questionnaire.returningPlayersDiv: 4 in div c 1 in div b
questionnaire.priorPlacement: 10/10 phenomenal job with how close div c east was

questionnaire.divisionPlacement: Div C for sure, Div B if deemed fit
questionnaire.priorPlacement: I think our placement was fair.
questionnaire.otherLeagues: We've played and will be playing in NEXO with Div C and B teams.
questionnaire.otherInfo: N/A
After setting up scrims with other teams I believe we are best suited for Div B
